criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women affected by one primary (no recurrent) monolateral ovarian endometrioma, with
             maximum diameter between 5 and 10 cm, undergoing laparoscopic enucleation by stripping
             technique;

          -  Normal AFC at the enrollment (baseline).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any other disease;

          -  Bilateral endometriomas;

          -  Deep infiltrating endometriosis;

          -  No previous pelvic surgery (even not gynecological);

          -  Any other pharmacologic and non pharmacologic treatment in the previous 3 months
             (wash-out period);
